  "texts": [
    "Regarding DL techniques, Huang et al. [28] proposed a CNN-based approach to analyze the intention of each sentence in bug report for the ease of reading the content.",
    "Li et al. [639] and Liu et al.",
    "[658] proposed auto-encoder networks with different structures for informative sentence extraction in bug reports.",
    "In recent studies, DL-based language models are also employed to automatically generate titles of bug reports [659,660].",
    "Bug localizationBug localization is the main BRM task facilitated by DL techniques, where 16 related papers are found."
